elim  : Π[ P ꞉ ∀ᴱ[ n ꞉ ℕ ] (Fin n → Type ℓ′) ]
        Π[ fz ꞉ ∀ᴱ[ n ꞉ ℕ ] P {suc n} fzero ]
        Π[ fs ꞉ ∀ᴱ[ n ꞉ ℕ ] ∀[ k ꞉ Fin n ] (P k → P (fsuc k)) ]
        ∀[ n ꞉ ℕ ] Π[ k ꞉ Fin n ] P k
elim P fz fs {x = suc n} (mk-fin 0) = fz
elim P fz fs {x = suc n} (mk-fin (suc k)) = fs (elim P fz fs (mk-fin k))

